 * length SOFT_MAX_BLOCK_LENGTH + MIN_BLOCK_LENGTH - 1, or when any block is of
 * length SOFT_MAX_BLOCK_LENGTH + 1 + DEFLATE_MAX_MATCH_LEN.  The latter case
